| 5 | **LOW** (3/10) | Escape key not tested for resetting new `checkinDate`/`parentId` state |

The existing tests are well-written and behavior-focused — the pattern for adding the missing coverage is already established. Minimum viable fix: add `vi.mock('../api', ...)`, add `fetchThings: vi.fn()` to `calendarDefaults`, and add one test each for the date path and parent relationship POST.
