eset not covered by test | LOW | Deferred to test improvement PR |\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Suggested Follow-up Issues\\n\\n1. **\\\"Refactor createThing to skip internal fetchThings when caller will refresh\\\"** (P3) — add optional `skipRefresh` flag to avoid double round-trips\\n2. **\\\"Replace hardcoded /api prefix in Sidebar with exported BASE constant\\\"** (P3) — eliminate magic string `/api/things/relationships`\\n\\n---\\n\\n*Resolved by Archon workflow `2f4bab79a67b16dab17a1e09b36befa7`*\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Disk space issue**: The device is full (`ENOSPC`), which prevented writing the `completion-report.md` artifact and running `gh issue comment`. You'll need to free up disk space to run any bash commands. Once space is available:\\n\\n```bash\\ngh issue comment 280 --repo alexsiri7/reli --body \\\"...\\\"\\n```\",\"cost_usd\":0.4100679,\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"num_turns\":24}"],"msg":"db.sqlite_query_failed"}
